{"tid":1940463,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"痛到行唔到 訓唔著","createTime":"2020-03-23T19:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T08:31:48.000Z","uid":228978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"04b6d2228fa8a1f1321eae3a2d225e183d28c208","tid":1940463,"uid":228978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:30:47.000Z","msg":"兩日前,我做咗幾set腳部運動<br />\n例如scissors,raised leg circle 等等<br />\n一直都冇咩事,係隻腳好似冇咩力<br />\n直到訓覺就開始仆街<br />\n兩隻腳一伸直就好痛<br />\n連帶上盤骨都好痛<br />\n點都訓唔著,訓咗都好易痛到醒返<br />\n而家日頭行路都有問題,企唔到直<br />\n行步路都痛到要烏低條腰<br />\n而家我又痛到訓唔著<br />\n上網查我好似係咩髖關節有事<br />\n有冇人可以話我知係咪真<br />\n同埋應該搵鐵打定去醫院(唔係咁想去醫院,呢個時勢去醫院好危)"},{"pid":"695a54483912a1a3cff9384d88ff2c0ec6fd739a","tid":1940463,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:33:46.000Z","msg":"係咪應該去搵個骨專科睇下"},{"pid":"5f08c56b8c38ad362fa79e6ec126259b1aa8a0c3","tid":1940463,"uid":228978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"695a54483912a1a3cff9384d88ff2c0ec6fd739a","tid":1940463,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:33:46.000Z","msg":"係咪應該去搵個骨專科睇下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:39:59.000Z","msg":"一開始唔覺咁嚴重,以為係普通扭傷<br />\n係去到而家先真係覺得大件事<br />\n有諗過睇骨專科,但要等聽日先"},{"pid":"1d17cec76dacb5b6cf18623d2da9daa68ddeb95d","tid":1940463,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:43:12.000Z","msg":"有冇捽野?"},{"pid":"98dd8ad6013ef9d0e485c419ffe07dced351097c","tid":1940463,"uid":228978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d17cec76dacb5b6cf18623d2da9daa68ddeb95d","tid":1940463,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:43:12.000Z","msg":"有冇捽野?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:46:52.000Z","msg":"有捽藥油,但作用唔大,仲係咁痛"},{"pid":"647a59a2f4acd75360cedef64babeeee9fe09e57","tid":1940463,"uid":82842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:47:04.000Z","msg":"仲拖 係到玩命 係我會睇西醫 起碼都照照x ray"},{"pid":"7a864ddc85db75906199bc5d6e0dda955e8b10fd","tid":1940463,"uid":155224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:50:14.000Z","msg":"去睇啦, 睇你講到好嚴重"},{"pid":"5b4248dd986a80007dfbd11f2934d2780705ede7","tid":1940463,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:50:31.000Z","msg":"物理治療！<br />\n<br />\n睇緊，之前又係過度運動，關節痛到行唔到2個禮拜<br />\n之後係到拖，呢1年黎，平時行路都痛<br />\n醫生話我on9拖足一年去醫，痛處延伸到上去<br />\n<br />\n所以巴打快d搵物理治療師<br />\n坊間d細鋪都ok了<br />\n<br />\n每次物理治療搵$300或樓下 最理想<br />\n針灸同物理治療師會幫你搞"},{"pid":"949225e40b1d0c7e04c5297d583f1450d6d94e31","tid":1940463,"uid":228978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"647a59a2f4acd75360cedef64babeeee9fe09e57","tid":1940463,"uid":82842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:47:04.000Z","msg":"仲拖 係到玩命 係我會睇西醫 起碼都照照x ray"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:51:39.000Z","msg":"原來真係咁嚴重"},{"pid":"afb3f82bb8814e581c5babbca17f0af24fe4fc6e","tid":1940463,"uid":228978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a864ddc85db75906199bc5d6e0dda955e8b10fd","tid":1940463,"uid":155224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:50:14.000Z","msg":"去睇啦, 睇你講到好嚴重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:52:11.000Z","msg":"會㗎啦"},{"pid":"c7f2327c8625eb62404fe2a88a42bba4b6d6ebcd","tid":1940463,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T19:54:44.000Z","msg":"物理治療師會評你邊忽最唔掂<br />\nmark低要照xray位置 寫信推介你去照<br />\n<br />\n你預成千到 xray<br />\n另外物理治療複診一個禮拜一次"},{"pid":"df876cdf6460d8246f3769acefd23ac877396c9d","tid":1940463,"uid":229020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T18:36:10.000Z","msg":"巴打我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088a862d047073d97480291c6b27c01a7a7ddaa8","tid":1940463,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T07:51:06.000Z","msg":"邊個位痛"},{"pid":"f97a459a7f137d6cbf8c2bd92ba9918b2ff37bd9","tid":1940463,"uid"